[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":277},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F":253,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F":262},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F04\u002F05\u002Fnodejs-mango-28-mongodb-compass-atlas-gui\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":232,"date":233,"description":18,"extension":234,"lang":235,"meta":236,"navigation":237,"path":238,"readingMinutes":239,"seo":240,"standalone":241,"stem":242,"tags":243,"tldr":250,"updated":250,"url":251,"__hash__":252},"content\u002F被迫吃芒果的前端工程師\u002F28-被迫吃芒果的前端工程師-Atlas-MongoDB-Compass-教學.md","(28)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - Atlas - MongoDB Compass 教學","475293919",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":227},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,34,40,43,49,52,58,61,67,70,76,79,85,88,108,111,114,120,127,143,146,155,158,163,166,172,182,185,193,196,202,205,211,214,220,223],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"前一章節已經申請了遠端的 MongoDB 資料庫，但我們該怎麼使用呢？所以這一章節就要來說明一下如何使用。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"mongodb-compass","MongoDB Compass",[16,24,25],{},"那我們該怎麼接上自己申請的遠端資料庫呢？其實最簡單就是使用 GUI 工具，而這邊就會建議使用官方所提供的 GUI 工具",[16,27,28],{},[29,30,22],"a",{"href":31,"rel":32},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.mongodb.com\u002Fproducts\u002Fcompass",[33],"nofollow",[16,35,36],{},[37,38],"img",{"alt":22,"src":39},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-27%2015.00.49.png",[16,41,42],{},"那麼該怎麼下載與安裝這邊就不說明了，所以這邊就直接進入 MongoDB Compass 介面",[16,44,45],{},[37,46],{"alt":47,"src":48},"MongoDB Compass 介面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-27%2015.46.59.png",[16,50,51],{},"看到英文一定會有相當多人害怕，因此這邊我提供 MongoDB Compass 翻譯畫面",[16,53,54],{},[37,55],{"alt":56,"src":57},"MongoDB Compass 翻譯","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2022-03-27_15_46_59.png",[16,59,60],{},"那麼我們就將我們申請的 MongoDB Atlas 連結，如果你找不到的話，回到這個頁面",[16,62,63],{},[37,64],{"alt":65,"src":66},"Database Deployments","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2023.06.52.png",[16,68,69],{},"上方有一個 Connect 按鈕，按下去之後它會問你，你要用哪一種方式連接 MongoDB",[16,71,72],{},[37,73],{"alt":74,"src":75},"連結方式","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-27%2016.35.41.png",[16,77,78],{},"而這邊我們要使用的就是 MongoDB Compass，因此就是選「Connect using MongoDB Compass」",[16,80,81],{},[37,82],{"alt":83,"src":84},"Connect using MongoDB Compass","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202203271638.png",[16,86,87],{},"點下去之後，他會進入到兩個選項",[89,90,91,100],"ul",{},[92,93,94,95],"li",{},"I do not have MongoDB Compass\n",[89,96,97],{},[92,98,99],{},"我沒有 MongoDB Compass",[92,101,102,103],{},"I have MongoDB Compass\n",[89,104,105],{},[92,106,107],{},"我有 MongoDB Compass",[16,109,110],{},"而這邊我們當然就是選擇「I have MongoDB Compass」，除非你前面都沒安裝。",[16,112,113],{},"當你點下「I have MongoDB Compass」之後，你就可以看到兩個資訊，第一個是我們 MongoDB Compass 版本，但因為我們是剛剛下載的，所以可以不動設定，第二個則是我們連接的 Url 請先複製下來",[16,115,116],{},[37,117],{"alt":118,"src":119},"複製","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202203271642.png",[16,121,122,123],{},"複製下來之後，你可以注意到畫面上有一個地方很特別，也就是 ",[124,125,126],"code",{},"\u003Cpassword>",[128,129,134],"pre",{"className":130,"code":131,"language":132,"meta":133,"style":133},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002Frayxu:\u003Cpassword>@cluster0.v7ywq.mongodb.net\u002Ftest\n","cmd","",[124,135,136],{"__ignoreMap":133},[137,138,141],"span",{"class":139,"line":140},"line",1,[137,142,131],{},[16,144,145],{},"這個密碼就是你前面所設定的使用者帳號密碼，因此正確來講會是這樣",[128,147,149],{"className":130,"code":148,"language":132,"meta":133,"style":133},"mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002F\u003Cusername>:\u003Cpassword>@cluster0.v7ywq.mongodb.net\u002Ftest\n",[124,150,151],{"__ignoreMap":133},[137,152,153],{"class":139,"line":140},[137,154,148],{},[16,156,157],{},"然後將上面連結貼到 MongoDB Compass 中",[16,159,160],{},[37,161],{"alt":22,"src":162},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202203271650.png",[16,164,165],{},"填上之後就可以看下 Connect 按鈕，過程會需要一點時間，所以要稍微等一下",[16,167,168],{},[37,169],{"alt":170,"src":171},"Connect...","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-27%2016.50.47.png",[16,173,174,175,178,179],{},"如果你連接之後發現錯誤，例如：",[124,176,177],{},"bad auth : Authentication failed.","、",[124,180,181],{},"connection \u003Cmonitor> to 16.163.80.186:27017 closed",[16,183,184],{},"這時候你可以注意一下是不是以下狀況",[89,186,187,190],{},[92,188,189],{},"有沒有把自己當前電腦 IP 加入到允許內",[92,191,192],{},"有沒有打錯帳號或密碼",[16,194,195],{},"連接成功之後，你可以看到畫面變成以下",[16,197,198],{},[37,199],{"alt":200,"src":201},"連接成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-27%2017.01.16.png",[16,203,204],{},"恭喜你，你已經連接上遠端的 MongoDB 資料庫了，那麼預設會有兩個 Database 資料庫，老樣子這邊一樣附上翻譯圖片",[16,206,207],{},[37,208],{"alt":209,"src":210},"翻譯圖片","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202203271712.png",[16,212,213],{},"接下來你可以試著點一下 local，裡面會有很多預設的 Collection 可以給你玩一下",[16,215,216],{},[37,217],{"alt":218,"src":219},"Default Collection","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-27%2017.15.00.png",[16,221,222],{},"那麼這邊也是一個基本的 MongoDB Compass 入門，大多時候來講我們會使用 MongoDB Compass 來看資料唷~",[224,225,226],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);backgrou